{
  "texts": [
    "Complementing HELM, BIG-Bench focuses on more specific and niche tasks that probe the boundaries of current LLM capabilities.",
    "With 204 tasks contributed from experts across fields, BIG-Bench was invaluable for testing specific tasks that were beyond the domain of HELM.",
    "Importantly, BIG-Bench provided niche tasks that have little overlap with other tasks, offering an unbiased perspective on subspace removal.",
    "Together, these datasets facilitate a comprehensive analysis of the influence of subspace removal on LLM performance across a spectrum of tasks.",
    "By integrating the thorough evaluation of HELM for general language abilities with the specialized tasks from BIG-Bench, this study explores how manipulation of tasks affects both broad and targeted model capabilities."
  ]
}